node.text:
Is your classroom in need of a makeover? When @thesuperheroteacher flips classrooms, she loves to include interactive bulletin boards. 

With this template, students in need of motivation can take a quote off the board, but they must replace it with their own words of encouragement. By the end of the year, all of the quotes featured are from students helping their peers.

Link in bio for the template!
